Job Details
A leading engineering company has been part of the developing the business in the oil and gas sector in UAE, requires a qualified and experienced Business Development Manager, Indian, having minimum 2 years in similar field in UAE.  The candidate should have excellent communication skills and have potential to bring business to the company.
Requirements
Bachelor’s degree in Engineering or any other equivalent
Fluency in Arabic is an added advantage
